                  </hi>. I am a wharfinger at the East and West India Docks—on 27th September last I received a case of leather belting marked W. W., which I saw handed to Edward Maybery on 7th October—this is the delivery order, authorising me to deliver it, it has Maybery's receipt on the back.</p>
