                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. SIMS</hi>. I ascertained lately that the goods were shipped to the Cape, which I communicated to the prosecutor—he ordered them for the Queensland market—they were shipped by Jacob Levy and Co.—I knew nothing of any arrangement between Smith and Levy—I have been told by Jacobs and Co. that I shall be paid.</p>
